the hidden eye is a 1945 american mystery film directed by richard whorf and written by george harmon &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; and harry ruskin . it is the sequel to the 1942 film eyes in the night . the film stars edward arnold , frances rafferty , ray collins , paul langton , william ' bill ' phillips and thomas e. jackson . the film was released on august 31 , 1945 , by metro-goldwyn-mayer .